WHAT THE SITE IS ABOUT:
Pageone is an IT/software firm that builds custom software for people - things like websites, mobile apps, and internal tools for clients. The hero section "Find quick solution with our Smart Search" is about helping visitors quickly find the right service for their problem. Use this as the theme for every page you build:
- Home = the hero pitch, inviting visitors to search for the service they need
- About us = who Pageone is, our mission, why clients should trust us
- Products = the software/services we build (e.g. Web Development, Mobile Apps, Custom Software, IT Consulting)
- Features = why clients pick us (e.g. Fast Delivery, Dedicated Support, Modern Tech Stack, Affordable Pricing)


